  "detailed_description": "<h1>Content Creation and Live Streaming Guide</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are free to create and stream content. However, it would be a great help to us if you could include a link to our store.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you.<br>For further inquiries, please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:anomalyguys@gmail.com\">anomalyguys@gmail.com</a>.</p></p><br><h1>Social Media</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/c6557d158f8fdaabb64ef37f668fec99.avif?t=1771905293\" width=616 height=130 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Check out the latest game news on our social media channels!</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/78a21d8bbafd1172bcdf24f2e93dc497.avif?t=1771905293\" width=800 height=240 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Info</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, a phone call rings at the GuGu Pizza shop...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Hello? This is the space station. Could you deliver 5 Hawaiian pizzas for us?” The owner doesn’t hesitate and packs the delivery boxes, deciding to send the pigeon deliveryman to space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, this delivery is no ordinary task. On the way to space with the pizza, there are dangers of falling, obstacles, and unpredictable challenges waiting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >『GuGu Pizza : Delivering Pizza to the Space Station? Boss, this is just not right!』 is a platformer challenge game where you deliver Hawaiian pizzas to a space station.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/3feadd711aa4b44e35462841f2255869.poster.avif?t=1771905293\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/3feadd711aa4b44e35462841f2255869.webm?t=1771905293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/3feadd711aa4b44e35462841f2255869.mp4?t=1771905293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep the pizza balanced and avoid falling!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s a game where you must climb while keeping the pizza balanced. Make sure to maintain its balance carefully so it doesn’t fall.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/d86c48622b4edf22c46712a08459304b.poster.avif?t=1771905293\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/d86c48622b4edf22c46712a08459304b.webm?t=1771905293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/d86c48622b4edf22c46712a08459304b.mp4?t=1771905293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch out for various obstacles and falling!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obstacles that hinder the pigeon delivering pizza are scattered everywhere, and you will lose the pizza if hit. You’ll also drop the pizza when falling from high places.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/0bb0cf5cc1d6afe8a0536034eefc261f.poster.avif?t=1771905293\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/0bb0cf5cc1d6afe8a0536034eefc261f.webm?t=1771905293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/0bb0cf5cc1d6afe8a0536034eefc261f.mp4?t=1771905293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump across various platforms and complete your pizza delivery mission.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/4ab7ab493fb16100c6644eef6dedf892.poster.avif?t=1771905293\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/4ab7ab493fb16100c6644eef6dedf892.webm?t=1771905293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/4ab7ab493fb16100c6644eef6dedf892.mp4?t=1771905293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There’s an assist mode to help your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If it feels too difficult, you can enable an assist mode to help with the pizza delivery. This activates an alternative way to play, suitable for players unfamiliar with this type of game.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Ready For Delivery</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready for delivery? Can you complete this perilous delivery and successfully bring the Hawaiian pizzas to the space station?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on your journey to space now!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/78a21d8bbafd1172bcdf24f2e93dc497.avif?t=1771905293\" width=800 height=240 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Info</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, a phone call rings at the GuGu Pizza shop...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Hello? This is the space station. Could you deliver 5 Hawaiian pizzas for us?” The owner doesn’t hesitate and packs the delivery boxes, deciding to send the pigeon deliveryman to space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, this delivery is no ordinary task. On the way to space with the pizza, there are dangers of falling, obstacles, and unpredictable challenges waiting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >『GuGu Pizza : Delivering Pizza to the Space Station? Boss, this is just not right!』 is a platformer challenge game where you deliver Hawaiian pizzas to a space station.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/3feadd711aa4b44e35462841f2255869.poster.avif?t=1771905293\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/3feadd711aa4b44e35462841f2255869.webm?t=1771905293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/3feadd711aa4b44e35462841f2255869.mp4?t=1771905293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep the pizza balanced and avoid falling!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It’s a game where you must climb while keeping the pizza balanced. Make sure to maintain its balance c