ay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/4ab7ab493fb16100c6644eef6dedf892.poster.avif?t=1771905293\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/4ab7ab493fb16100c6644eef6dedf892.webm?t=1771905293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308560/extras/4ab7ab493fb16100c6644eef6dedf892.mp4?t=1771905293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There’s an assist mode to help your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If it feels too difficult, you can enable an assist mode to help with the pizza delivery. This activates an alternative way to play, suitable for players unfamiliar with this type of game.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Ready For Delivery</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready for delivery? Can you complete this perilous delivery and successfully bring the Hawaiian pizzas to the space station?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on your journey to space now!</p>",
